        "subject": "LU-7887 build: revert of use \"make rpms\" for building Lustre RPMs",
        "message": "LU-7887 build: revert of use \"make rpms\" for building Lustre RPMs\n\nTesting the theory that recent lustre-init fails of all sles builds\nis really a build problem introduced by the lbuild change.\nIf the theory proves true will need a fix in current lbuild.\n\nThis revert is only for testing purposes, not to be landed.\n\nTest-Parameters: mdsdistro=sles11sp4 ossdistro=sles11sp4 \\\n  clientdistro=sles11sp4 mdsfilesystemtype=ldiskfs \\\n  mdtfilesystemtype=ldiskfs ostfilesystemtype=ldiskfs \\\n  testgroup=review-ldiskfs fortestonly\n\nSigned-off-by: Bob Glossman <bob.glossman@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Icc88852fdea4c7195e69ce977b09170fe61c1412\n"
